		<title>Writing an Article vs. Writing a Blog Post: What&#8217;s the Difference?</title>
		<link>http://www.makealivingwriting.com/writing-an-article-vs-writing-blog-post-differences/</link>
		<comments>http://www.makealivingwriting.com/writing-an-article-vs-writing-blog-post-differences/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2015 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Carol Tice]]></dc:creator>
