		<title>Top 3 Clueless Comments Freelance Writers Get &#8212; and How to Respond</title>
		<link>http://www.makealivingwriting.com/3-clueless-comments-freelance-writers-get/</link>
		<comments>http://www.makealivingwriting.com/3-clueless-comments-freelance-writers-get/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Wed, 17 Dec 2014 10:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Editor]]></dc:creator>
				<category><![CDATA[Blog]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[freelance writing]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[guest post]]></category>
